{
  "stem": "210.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had, like, faucets, different faucets, one next to the other, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you just have to go after.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You stayed there outside for all this time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then you had to go and wash yourself, shower.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not a shower.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just wash yourself, you know, under this thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had to wash your head, your whole body.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was no soap-- just with the water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then you put back this dress.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You didn't even dry yourself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was certain times that you could go to the-- excuse me-- to the toilet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was like holes in the-- on a site someplace with very little privacy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was just one next to the other, and there was just like a wall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But from-- this is how-- this were our toilets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you could only go a certain time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was there for 11 days or 12 days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, they made us go up, And one, when we sent for after they counted us, they told us to, you know, make rows over there, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they yelled and screamed and kicked you and hit you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was just horrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, you ran for your life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They assessed you with their rifle butts and that the women screamed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just like chaos.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you wound up in these rows.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was among them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we're going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We thought maybe they're taking us to, you know-- and the first night that we got there in Auschwitz and the barracks had like, like a chimney in the middle of the-- and there was this-- she was like a kapo or somebody.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she would scream and yell.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
